data.description: This stunning property boasts three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a bonus room, all conveniently located within walking distance of the lake. The extensive amenities include a two-car garage, RV parking, and a spacious horseshoe driveway, offering ample space for recreational vehicles. Upon entry, you are greeted by a generously sized living room complete with a beautiful rock fireplace, perfect for unwinding and relaxing. The backyard features a large patio area complemented by a block wall, providing an ideal setting for privacy. Additionally, Spring Valley Lake offers an array of recreational opportunities, including a fantastic beach and park area, as well as an exclusive country club with amenities such as golf, a pool, weight room, restaurant, banquet hall, tennis courts, stables, and much more. This exceptional property is sure to attract considerable interest, so do not delay and call today to schedule your visit!
